attchmntText: Media Release
Mastek Limited has informed the Exchange regarding Allotment of 25047  Shares.
Reliance Power Limited has informed the Exchange regarding a press release dated August 24, 2025, titled "Media Release".
United Spirits Limited has informed the Exchange regarding 'Clarification in relation to 26th AGM Notice'.
APL Apollo Tubes Limited has informed the Exchange regarding Newspaper Advertisement of completion of despatch of the Notice of 40th Annual General Meeting.

NTPC Limited has informed the Exchange about disclosure dt. 22.08.2025 made by our subsidiary NTPC Green Energy Limited regarding the declaration of COD of the part capacity of 50 MW (Solar) by a group company of our subsidiary NTPC Green Energy Limited w.e.f. 24.08.2025.
Britannia Industries Limited has informed the Exchange regarding Change in Director(s) of the company.
Railtel Corporation Of India Limited has informed the Exchange about Bagging/Receiving of orders/contracts
Reliance Communications Limited has informed the Exchange about Fraud/Default/Arrest
IRIS Business Services Limited has submitted a clarification on Rating Report issued by India Ratings & Research.
Ola Electric Mobility Limited has submitted with the exchange a copy of voting results of 08th Annual General Meeting held on August 22, 2025.
Osia Hyper Retail Limited has informed the Exchange regarding  Board meeting held on August 23, 2025.
Cybertech Systems And Software Limited has informed the Exchange about Copy of Newspaper Publication of Information regarding 30th AGM
Cybertech Systems And Software Limited has informed the Exchange about Copy of Newspaper Publication regarding 100 days campaign by IEPF Authority
Global Surfaces Limited has informed the Exchange about Letters being sent to shareholders pursuant to Regulation 36(1)(b) of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements), 2015
Ethos Limited has informed the Exchange regarding Notice of Annual General Meeting to be held on September 15, 2025 at 11:00 AM (1ST) through Video Conference/Other Audio Visual Means
Bella Casa Fashion & Retail Limited has informed the Exchange regarding Notice of Annual General Meeting to be held on September 16, 2025

Pursuant to Regulation 30 of SEBI (LODR) Regulations, 2015, Electronics Mart India Limited has informed the exchange regarding the sale of its "IQ" division, comprising four "IQ" retail stores of the Company, along with the registered trademarks "IQ" on a going concern basis, to Angel Teletech Private Limited, effective 23rd August 2025.
Trident Limited has submitted the Exchange a copy Srutinizers report of  Annual General Meeting held on August 23, 2025
Orient Green Power Company Limited has informed the Exchange about Transcript
